after each sentence

*Večer*as sam se šetao pored reke. (I was walking by the river in the evening.)

*Večer*om sam se vratio kući. (I returned home in the evening.)

U *veče*r sam započeo svoj projekat. (I started my project in the evening.)

*Večer*om sam imao sastanak s kolegama. (I had a meeting with colleagues in the evening.)

*Večer*u sam proveo uz knjigu. (I spent the evening with a book.)